<div class="inline-citation" id="cite-Gothic" style="display:none;width: 240px">
<a class="quiet" href="javascript:hidecite('cite-Gothic')" style="font-size:90%"><img src="../../../icons/eks.png" alt="[x]" style="float:right;clear:both;margin:1px"></a>
<p style="margin:0ex">Ruskin, John. "The Nature of Gothic", in <span class="ital">The Stones of Venice, Volume II: The Sea-Stories</span> Mineola: Dover Phoenix Editions, 2005.</p>
</div>
<div class="inline-citation" id="cite-MCE" style="display:none;width: 240px">
